    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市领头羊的衰退对未来回报来说是个坏兆头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/europe-s-stock-leaders-are-fading-in-bad-sign-for-future-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市连续两年上涨的动力正在减弱，在经济增长放缓和中美紧张局势引发投资者信心考验之际，该地区股市面临空白。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/europe-s-stock-leaders-are-fading-in-bad-sign-for-future-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国连续两周遭遇坏消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/germany-struggles-with-two-terrible-weeks-of-bad-news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国挺过了新冠疫情，并在俄罗斯切断天然气供应后避免了灾难性的工业停工。尽管如此，这仍未完全消除人们对未来可能出现经济困境的担忧。过去两周的情况提供了戏剧性的证据，证明这些担忧是有道理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/germany-struggles-with-two-terrible-weeks-of-bad-news</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Sep 2024 06:59:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
